EU’s Barroso Says Revamped Efsf Can Help Prevent Contagion

-- B y   J o n e s   H a y d e n
-- 
2011-10-10T13:51:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-10/eu-s-barroso-says-revamped-efsf-can-help-prevent-contagion.html
European Commission President  Jose
Barroso  said the revamped European Financial Stability Facility
will help prevent contagionin the euro area and urged its
ratification by parliaments.  “I hope that will happen soon,” Barroso said today in
Brussels. “Then the fund will be able to contribute to
recapitalizing banks.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jones Hayden at 
 jhayden1@bloomberg.net  